---
title: Middle Eastern Lamb Koftas with Yoghurt & Garlic-Herb Roast Veggie Toss
description: Spice up your dinner with these juicy Middle Eastern lamb koftas, packed with bold flavours. Served alongside a creamy dollop of tangy yoghurt and a vibrant garlic-herb roast veggie toss, this dish is the perfect balance of hearty, fresh and absolutely delicious. A little exotic, a lot delicious - get ready to savour every bite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
